---
title: Item Pipeline — du scan au merge
---
flowchart LR
    scan([backlog scan\nBacklogSources])
    pending[(⬜ pending\npriority 0→5)]
    claim([claim_next\npriority DESC])
    worktree([git worktree\n+ tmux window])
    skill_run([skill-run\nclaude -p])
    push([git push\n+ gh pr create])
    pr_open[(🔵 pr_open\nattend review)]
    ci([CI\nGitHub Actions])
    review([Review\néquipe])
    done[(✅ done\nworktree cleanup)]

    judge([Judge\nautolearn])
    retry[(⬜ pending\nretry_count++)]
    skip[(⏭ skipped)]

    scan -->|reconcile_backlog| pending
    pending --> claim
    claim -->|Reconciler 120s| worktree
    worktree --> skill_run

    skill_run -->|succès| push
    push --> pr_open
    pr_open --> ci
    ci --> review
    review -->|approved + merge| done

    skill_run -->|échec| judge
    judge -->|retryable| retry
    retry --> claim
    judge -->|non retryable| skip

    ci -->|red| pr_open

